Package org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.model

Class Summary
Group The model class representing group memberships for a user.
PayPalPayment A Faces managed bean that supports the PayPal payment page
RegisterForAbrc A Faces Managed Bean that models the registration feature for ABRC ABRC requires these elements: Right now we are collecting: First name Last name Email Phone Job Title Billing Address (lab address) Shipping Address (person address) Username Password Lab Name ("School name" because this is for teachers buying education kits from TAIR from a location external to TAIR)
Registration A Data Transfer Object containing shared elements relating to registrations in TAIR, including basic subscription information as well as ABRC-related registration information, which is all optional.
SubscribeGroup A Faces managed bean that manages the model information for a group of TAIR users being subscribed at once for a discount.
SubscribeNew A Faces Managed Bean that models the subscription information for a new user
SubscribeRegistered A Faces Managed Bean that models the subscription for a registered user.
Subscription A helper class that models subscription characteristics.
 

Enum Summary
Group.Role A set of enumerated type values corresponding to paywall roles played by users.
Subscription.Term An enumeration for the various subscription terms
